## Geography

We supply foundries across Russia and neighbouring countries. Our logistics are planned to deliver materials on time and in the required quantities, taking into account:

- seasonal changes in production load;
- planned shutdowns and maintenance;
- stock level requirements and product shelf life.

The goal is simple: no downtime because the foundry has run out of binders, coatings or auxiliaries.

## Intema Group in numbers

Our product range is built around real foundry needs:

- **3 main product lines:** binder systems, coatings and auxiliary materials.
- **10+ casting processes** we support: alpha-set, furan, cold-box, croning, lost foam, no-bake, permanent mould, sodium silicate, resol-CO₂, Pep-set and others.
- **2 coating bases:** water-based and alcohol-based.
- **5 main fillers:** zircon, graphite, magnesite, aluminosilicate, chromite.
- **8 types of auxiliaries:** AIPS (alcohol for coatings), adhesives, modifiers, cleaning and release agents, repair pastes, sealing cords, exothermic products.

The catalogue and filters are structured so that engineers can quickly find relevant materials for a given process, alloy and casting requirement.

